{"hash":"1abbbfc2b35e75b7958fa182c4e90f4fc6e772d0","data":{"post":{"title":"7 tips to get started with Sitecore Commerce 9","description":"7 tips to get started with Sitecore Commerce 9","date":"March 29, 2018","timeToRead":2,"content":"<style>\nol li { font-weight: bold;}\nol li p,\nol li pre,\nol li span,\nol li ol li {\n\tfont-weight: normal;\n\tmargin-top:0px;\n}\n</style>\n<p>Here are some tips to help you get started after installing Sitecore Experience Commerce 9 Update-1:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Commerce Business Tools</strong></p>\n<p>There's a new icon added to your launchpad which is how to navigate into the backend commerce system.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 433 372' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-b0e294ea31ed2547110ebe96754eddbb'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-b0e294ea31ed2547110ebe96754eddbb)' width='433' height='372' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%%2bmvXrynb23e//DKwumsIQLXU1tZC7v96/sK5019Kjx544ef/xsbx0rvkGDC4QGD9esHt22fOnfvq%2bHHdvT/Yw5yDlZSWFxeX3g1gMIv5vPvmLlq5Yt6yZfOXLF5Wwi8t5hcVF7NmBub/NSb1VTIhShgHuMSbGPd1Fns/G9uPYftI3pskeYAgD5DkQR55iMJhPsKRHIqzOMon3ynlZVHGe3c6vDMB%2bCP9crBDHiEJwOHh9hCAQDhIEAfwsXiLizPkRVgbm6PgEgoOV4ETSi6u4OJtXK6SwNUkruERAC2f0NHg4Xo%2bYeDhhmLoE9Yy0lFJ2itRC3ACqkjnXB7dOqpIB91W8RwVBK1jryBA314F4KG2HKd17NQSSwmhxblaHNNxOQANF1NzEJQYpmBDnKMgZ2HyIjajEeMKWGwBG2vi8QVMZkNBkYDFasLYQlaREGNBK%2bZiIqxIwmEDpDxcimPNJC7hsltJTEUyVSUcdSlHXYxp%2bCxtGa6rJDTFmLaUo%2bEzteVcdXGRBs2yNRWEppzQlHE1FSS0MKImizTFbN2CUjW/iBphqnlMccEcgJSLSXGOhIuJOQhCDtbIngACFtYABEQFRbIHlrYfOKR4eKVu02bVLx6XP/CztvnzlCtWKJcu1qxZ1Tb3PvXDK1WLH9AsX9pKEva3Dlq3bVLNqzQvWdix9nHLgwuh0756mfXhpY4Na9tXLWl/dLn1wcX2px8zLyyz/XKNdfnCjp%2bvMJRyXHu2dB9%2bq3Pv89aHFlgfWeaore56/fWufbs6HlthWTKv44lHjKtWaFY/ont0VRsfl3HYLVyshYM1cz